MultiPixel DMCA & Reporting Portal Guide
Relimintor (Raptor4 / MultiPixel)

1. PURPOSE
This guide explains how to report violations.

2. REPORTABLE ISSUES
• copyright violations
• server violations
• mod violations
• impersonation
• safety issues
• cheating/exploits
• monetization violations

3. HOW TO REPORT
Reports must include:
• description of issue
• evidence (screenshots, logs, links)
• your contact information
• server/mod name
• timestamps

4. DMCA REPORTS
DMCA reports must include:
• your legal name
• your contact information
• description of copyrighted work
• description of infringing content
• sworn statement of accuracy

5. MULTIPIXEL ACTIONS
MultiPixel may:
• remove content
• ban servers
• revoke approvals
• issue DMCA takedowns
• pursue legal action
